title: Anthony Weiner Gets Advice
description:
Written by James McCarthy
Starring: Dan Hodapp, Avery Monsen, Zack Phillips, Lisa Kleinman, Langan Kingsley, Jon Bershad.

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 5, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
